{"tid":942971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天降銀紙】幣少爺重返黃金商場 坐林寶堅尼親自派錢","createTime":"2018-12-16T07:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T07:58:56.000Z","uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4c5a963893b730ab6658424c347dc7990937c0","tid":942971,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:58:32.000Z","msg":"On9仔搏拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n被指是撒錢事件幕後搞手的「幣少爺」黃鉦傑，昨晚在fb貼文揚言會在今午到明哥飯店買慈善買飯票派比老人家後，今午駕駛林寶堅尼超跑離開西貢寓所，抵達深水埗區後，卻未有直接駛去明哥飯店，反而重返黃金商場門外，親自向途人派錢。"},{"pid":"a3b867f8879b1ec141194f8b30871f4d7bdec6e3","tid":942971,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181216/59036292%20%20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59036292%2520%2520&d=2DedmL28IKyHTBDmuYRUIHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=98b892d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59036292%2520%2520&h=405ff800\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181216/59036292%20%20</a>"}]}